<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6130> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6130" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "No title preserved. Assigned by Brutus to guard C. Antonius (see Promagistrates), he became late in 43 or early in 42 his executioner (Dio 47.24.2 and 4). See 42, Prefects. See above, Promagistrates, on C. Antonius." .
